        "body": "## Summary\n\n- repair additive SQLite state schema upgrades uncovered during live inference testing on an older state DB\n- honor `OPENAI_BASE_URL` / `ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL` defaults across OpenAI, Anthropic, and native PDF paths\n- honor OpenRouter Anthropic cache retention for `long` / `none` without forwarding OpenAI-incompatible cache params\n- make `apply_patch` provider-neutral while preserving explicit disable and allow-model gates\n- let provider-scoped configure cleanup show and prune stale configured model allowlist entries\n- expose GitHub Copilot bundled thinking policy so dashboard/offline policy lookups retain xhigh-capable profiles\n\nRefs #74427, #74432, #79370, #88359, #88357, #45269, #80366, #80347, #79894.\n\n## Verification\n\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/state/openclaw-state-db.test.ts -- --reporter=verbose`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs extensions/openai/base-url.test.ts extensions/openai/openai-provider.test.ts src/agents/anthropic-transport-stream.test.ts src/agents/tools/pdf-native-providers.test.ts -- --reporter=verbose`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/prompt-cache-retention.test.ts src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/extra-params.openrouter-cache-control.test.ts src/agents/embedded-agent-runner-extraparams-openrouter.test.ts src/agents/anthropic-payload-policy.test.ts src/llm/providers/stream-wrappers/proxy.test.ts src/llm/providers/stream-wrappers/anthropic-cache-control-payload.test.ts -- --reporter=verbose`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/agents/agent-tools.create-openclaw-coding-tools.test.ts src/agents/agent-tools-agent-config.test.ts -- --reporter=verbose`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/commands/model-picker.test.ts src/commands/configure.gateway-auth.prompt-auth-config.test.ts -- --reporter=verbose`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs extensions/github-copilot/provider-policy-api.test.ts extensions/github-copilot/index.test.ts extensions/github-copilot/models.test.ts -- --reporter=verbose -t \"provider-policy-api|xhigh|reasoning efforts|static overrides\"`\n- `pnpm check:changed` via Blacksmith Testbox `tbx_01kt3em5r9vd7g0bnykrff6jdk` (provider `blacksmith-testbox`, exit 0)\n\n## Notes\n\n- PR #88941 was closed separately as already fixed on current main by #88932 handling; this branch does not include that broader strip-thinking implementation.\n- Issue #88201 is not closed by this branch; live Anthropic baseline and current-source local inference remain materially different enough to keep it open.\n",
